The paper [BIB/Gerdt_93a] contains a description of the ASYS package, version 2, and 18 more or less simple examples from the literature for test and comparison purposes. Contains only run time comparisons. It discusses the following examples:
Gerdt-85 as example 1 Gerdt-91a as example 2 Gerdt-91b as example 3 Gerdt-90 as example 4 Cyclic_5 as example 5 Cyclic_5_1 as example 6 Cyclic_7_1 as example 7 Katsura_4 as example 8 Katsura_5 as example 9 Katsura_6 as example 10 Trinks as example 11 Sym1_321 as example 12 Gerdt-93 as example 13 Caprasse as example 14 Hairer_1 as example 15 Czapor-91 as example 17
